        <profile name="Field Reforging" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="4023-aca9-bc37-6e1d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Move step, select up to 2 different friendly units within 9” of and visible to this unit. Then, for each selected unit, roll 1 D6 for each of that unit’s missing Health. If you selected two units, that unit Repairs 1 for each result of 5+. If you selected one unit, that unit instead Repairs 1 for each result of 4+.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
